=head1 NAME

_FILL_ZPD_MAP_ - fills gaps in a ZPD map

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _FILL_ZPD_MAP_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive runs thresh and fillbad.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

None.

=head1 EXTERNAL TASKS

KAPPA.

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

None

=head1 OUTPUT FILES

None.

=head1 NOTES

None.

